suffering out of ingratitude

578
00:47:45,142 --> 00:47:47,766
simply to convince himself
that he is a man

579
00:47:47,850 --> 00:47:49,766
and not a piano key.

580
00:47:52,683 --> 00:47:54,559
Hard to understand, right?

