590
00:48:26,517 --> 00:48:29,392
And they sold us
what we wanted,

591
00:48:29,475 --> 00:48:31,475
self and happiness,

592
00:48:31,559 --> 00:48:33,392
which the 9 provides in spades

593
00:48:33,475 --> 00:48:36,933
