608
00:49:27,600 --> 00:49:28,725
Some.

609
00:49:28,808 --> 00:49:31,850
Are you hungry?
I don't have much.

610
00:49:35,058 --> 00:49:36,434
How 'bout your parents?

611
00:49:36,517 --> 00:49:38,891
Can you remember them?

612
00:49:41,017 --> 00:49:45,808
I was raised by Eels to be an Eel,
pretending to be a Native.

613
00:49:45,891 --> 00:49:49,058
We read books, watched films...

614
00:49:49,142 --> 00:49:50,933
