00:52:03,975 --> 00:52:06,475
- ( plays softly )
- Here.

635
00:52:07,559 --> 00:52:10,434
Put this one here on top.

636
00:52:10,517 --> 00:52:14,475
Yeah. Yeah, that's it.
Try it.

